353
00:14:41.060 --> 00:14:42.700
Peki ya Kral Maymun?

354
00:14:42.700 --> 00:14:44.000
Ona ihtiyacımız yok.

355
00:14:44.000 --> 00:14:44.900
Hadi gidelim.

356
00:14:44.900 --> 00:14:46.500
Yolculuk!

357
00:14:46.500 --> 00:14:47.300
Su ejderhası!

358
00:14:47.300 --> 00:14:58.300
Gücü açın!

359
00:15:03.920 --> 00:15:04.840
Gücü açın!

360
00:15:04.840 --> 00:15:17.520
